00:01:42.110 --> 00:01:46.190
It's an approximate thing,
because we approximated

00:01:46.190 --> 00:01:47.450
the Bessel function.

00:01:47.450 --> 00:01:49.130
This is exact.

00:01:49.130 --> 00:01:56.360
This equation is
